thread.title: Martellus Bennett compares Jay Cutler to Jesus
thread.title_full: Martellus Bennett compares Jay Cutler to Jesus - NY Daily News

author: NEW YORK DAILY NEWS
title: Martellus Bennett compares Jay Cutler to Jesus
text:
Charles Rex Arbogast/AP Martellus Bennet compared Jay Cutler to Jesus and Keanu Reeves. Martellus Bennet went Biblical on Sunday’s win.
The Chicago tight end compared Jay Cutler to Jesus Christ — after the quarterback returned from an injury to lead the Bears to a win.
Bennett was defending the embattled quarterback after the Bears pulled off a wild 22-20 win over the Oakland Raiders on Sunday, according to the Chicago Sun-Times.
